rows.label: tev035901_SEL0011
rows.name: Ask Veverta about her work.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev035901_JNK0020
rows.name: Discuss[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev035901_SEL0021
rows.name: Ask Veverta if she's heard any interesting rumors.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev035901_SEL0031
rows.name: Ask Veverta about languages.

rows.label: tev035901_SEL0041
rows.name: Ask Veverta what she plans to do next.

rows.label: tev035901_SEL1021
rows.name: Ask Veverta about recent developments.

rows.label: tev035901_MSG0001
rows.name:
It seems like loads of Ma-non have managed to find
work in your city already, doesn't it?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev035901_MSG0002
rows.name:
After all, there are lots of ways we can help BLADE
out with with Ma-non technology, don't you think?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev035901_MSG0003
rows.name:
...What, me? Oh, I don't plan to work. Work is tiring,
you know?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev035901_MSG0004
rows.name:
Why bother working when I can live on the ship and
let my mother and father take care of of me?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev035901_MSG0005
rows.name:
This way I get to wander the streets and and chat with
interesting folks like you. That seems like a much better
life, doesn't it?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev035901_MSG0008
rows.name:
Panyar and I haven't been able to hang out at all
since we got to NLA, you know?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev035901_MSG0009
rows.name:
She's so caught up in human fashion that she spends
more time shopping than than she does with with me!
Isn't that pathetic?![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev035901_MSG0010
rows.name:
I don't get it. Why don't we all wear the same thing?
And why is she so darn interested in fashion anyway?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev035901_MSG0015
rows.name:
I can understand every word that comes out of your
mouth, but I can't read Earth writing to save my life.
Which is really odd, isn't it?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev035901_MSG0016
rows.name:
Thankfully, some Ma-non genius came up with an auto-
translator that displays comm devices in a language
I can actually read. So so so great, yes?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev035901_MSG0017
rows.name:
But even without the terminals, humans are pretty
helpful about explaining what different things say,
aren't they? So I manage to to get by.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev035901_MSG0018
rows.name:
What I can't figure out is why we can converse at all.
Let's see a a Ma-non genius solve that one, right?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev035901_MSG0023
rows.name:
I've seen a lot of species try and stand up to the
Ganglion, you know? But they didn't last long.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev035901_MSG0024
rows.name:
You humans basically made history by sending those
bullies packing, didn't you? And to think that I got
to see it with with my own eyes.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev035901_MSG0025
rows.name:
I wish there was some way to tell the whole universe
about it. Maybe snazz the story up a bit and make it
really fun?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev035901_MSG0026
rows.name:
I think I'm on to something here, don't you?
...Wait, is this what it means to want to work?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev035901_MSG0011
rows.name: Sounds like the undies didn't work out, did they?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev035901_MSG0012
rows.name:
Well, in related news, Panyar sent me this "perfume"
stuff she she came up with instead...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev035901_MSG0013
rows.name:
It smells nice, don't you think? Also, I thought it might
put me in a working mood, so I went ahead and
lathered up good.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev035901_MSG0014
rows.name:
But I think I overdid it, actually? The stuff smelled so
great I kind of of of fell asleep.[ST:wait ]
